      public User(String userID, String name, String email, String phoneNumber, String city, String password, Role role, boolean isActive)
      Instantiates a new user with the specified details.
      Parameters:
      userID - the user ID
      name - the name of the user
      email - the email address of the user
      phoneNumber - the phone number of the user
      city - the city where the user resides
      password - the password for the user's account
      role - the role assigned to the user
      isActive - the active status of the user
